    <summary>Space-themed pinball game</summary>
    <description>**SpaceCadetPinball** is a decompilation of the game that was bundled with Windows XP.

### Installation

This is a portable package (not installing).

The default installation directory is `C:\ProgramData\chocolatey\lib\spacecadetpinball`.

A start menu shortcut is created in a folder named "Game".

Options and high score are purposefully *not* be removed during uninstalling. These are stored in `%AppData%\SpaceCadetPinball\imgui_pb.ini`. Remove the directory manually if desired.</description>
    <releaseNotes>Feature release focusing on FT compatibility

Main highlights:
* FT: collision system changes, table control changes, multiball, three MIDI tracks.
* HW accelerated ImGui renderer.
* Work in progress: localization support. Depends on external font selection for non-Latin languages.
* Experimental stereo sound support.
* UX improvements.
* Bug fixes.</releaseNotes>
